sub_title: M.B.A & Master of Science in Entrepreneurship
summary: Results-oriented professional and target-oriented sales manager with 7 years' experience across the FMCG industry in South America. Proven success in building and maintaining a loyal client base while crafting high-impact solutions to drive business development. Strengths in logistics, purchasing and sales backed by M.B.A and Msc in Entrepreneurship. Driven to succeed; an expert in research and with a deep passion for trading. Helping start-ups since July 2020 in Colombia and the Netherlands.
